boardcam

Class BoardMachine

  • java.lang.Object
    • boardcam.BoardMachine

  • public class BoardMachine
extends java.lang.Object
    Machine interface for cutting boards (nurbs surfaces) Works for 3 and 4 axis machines Requires the file shapebot.properties to be located in BoardCAD's home dir Also requires an stl-model of the cutter to be located in the same dir
